inside 
`xml_binding_build`

so that the resulting xjc would look like this 

    &lt;xjc package=&quot;mypackage&quot; destdir=&quot;build/generated/jaxbCache/mypackage&quot; catalog=&quot;catalog.xml&quot;&gt;
                &lt;classpath&gt;
                    &lt;pathelement location=&quot;${src.dir}&quot;/&gt;
