You can implement just one, say `findMax`, and pass it a [`Comparator`](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/Comparator.html) that indicates how comparisons should be done:

    private int findMax(Comparator&lt;Integer&gt; comparator) {
        int max = arr[0];
        for (int num : arr) {
            if (comparator.compare(num, max) &gt; 0) {
                max = num;
